<h2>Cocktails</h2>

    <h3>Margarita</h3>

    <ul>3 oz Tequila</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Triple Sec</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Sour Mix</ul>

    <ol>Grab a pint glass and pour the ingredients in</ol>
    <ol>Add ice and shake</ol>
    <ol>Grab a margarita glass, rim as needed</ol>
    <ol>Pour cocktail into the glass and garnish with a lime wheel</ol>

    <h3>Mojito</h3>

    <ul>3 oz Rum</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Lime Juice</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Agave</ul>
    <ul>Mint leaves</ul>
    <ul>Club Soda</ul>

    <ol>Grab a pint glass and muddle 4-5 mint leaves</ol>
    <ol>Pour ingredients in pint glass</ol>
    <ol>Add ice and shake</ol>
    <ol>Grab a Collins glass and pour cocktail</ol>
    <ol>Top off with club soda and a lime wedge</ol>

    <h3>Hugo Spritz</h3>

    <ul>2 oz Sauvigon Blanc</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz St. Germain</ul>
    <ul>Club Soda</ul>
    <ul>Mint Leaves</ul>
    <ul>Lemon Wedges</ul>

    <ol>Grab a pint glass and muddle 4-5 mint leaves and 2-3 slices of lemon</ol>
    <ol>Pour ingredients in pint glass</ol>
    <ol>Add ice and shake</ol>
    <ol>Grab a wine glass and pour cocktail</ol>
    <ol>Top off with club soda and a lime wedge</ol>

    <h3>Coconut Martini</h3>

    <ul>1.5 oz Coconut Rum</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Vanilla Vodka</ul>
    <ul>0.5 oz Coconut Puree</ul>
    <ul>0.25 oz Pineapple Juice</ul>
    <ul>Coconut Flakes</ul>

    <ol>Grab a pint glass and pour ingredients</ol>
    <ol>Add ice and shake</ol>
    <ol>Grab a chilled martini glass and strain cocktail</ol>
    <ol>Garnish with coconut flakes</ol>

    <h3>Paloma</h3>

    <ul>3 oz Agave Tequila</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Lime Juice</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Agave</ul>
    <ul>0.5 oz Grapefruit Juice</ul>
    <ul>Club Soda</ul>

    <ol>Grab a pint glass and pour ingredients</ol>
    <ol>Add ice and shake</ol>
    <ol>Grab a Collins glass and pour cocktail</ol>
    <ol>Top off with club soda and a lime wedge</ol>

    <h3>Mudslide</h3>

    <ul>1.5 oz Kahlua</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Irish Cream</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Vanilla Vodka</ul>
    <ul>0.5 oz Heavy Cream</ul>
    <ul>Chocolate Syrup</ul>

    <ol>Grab a blender and add all ingredients</ol>
    <ol>Add ice and blend</ol>
    <ol>Grab a Collins glass and decorate with chocolate syrup</ol>
    <ol>Pour blended cocktail into glass</ol>

    <h3>Sangria</h3>

    <ul>1.5 oz Red or White Wine</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Sour Mix</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Brandy</ul>
    <ul>1 Tbsp Sugar</ul>
    <ul>Chopped Apple and Oranges</ul>
    <ul>Club Soda</ul>

    <ol>Grab a pint glass and grab 2 tong-fulls of chopped apples and oranges</ol>
    <ol>Pour brandy, sour mix, and sugar into the pint glass</ol>
    <ol>Add ice, top off with wine and shake</ol>
    <ol>Grab a wine glass and pour cocktail</ol>
    <ol>Top off with club soda</ol>

    <h3>Bloody Mary</h3>

    <ul>3 oz Bloody Mary Mix</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Vodka</ul>
    <ul>1.5 oz Lemon Juice</ul>
    <ul>Celery</ul>
    <ul>Olives</ul>
    <ul>Lemon Wedge</ul>
    <ul>Lime Wedge</ul>
    

    <ol>Grab a pint glass and add ice</ol>
    <ol>Pour ingredients in pint glass</ol>
    <ol>Garnish with celery, olives, lemon, and lime</ol>

    <h3>Old Fashioned</h3>

    <ul>1.5 oz Bourbon Whiskey</ul>
    <ul>1 Sugar Cube</ul>
    <ul>1 Cherry</ul>
    <ul>Orange Peel</ul>
    <ul>Bitters</ul>

    <ol>Grab a rocks glass and muddle orange peel, cherry, and sugar cube</ol>
    <ol>Pour bourbon in glass</ol>
    <ol>Add 2-3 dashes of bitters</ol>
    <ol>Add ice and stir</ol>
